text: Tracy Austin (born 12 December 1962, in Palos Verdes, California) is a former American tennis player. She is youngest ever US Open female singles champion and the youngest person to become a member in the International Tennis Hall of Fame. == References == Category:1962 births Category:American tennis players Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Los Angeles County, California Category:US Open (tennis) champions Category:World No. 1 tennis players
